snippet.title: [MAME] Disney Tennis + Face Chase (JAKKS Game Key) (c)2005 JAKKS Pacific
snippet.description: SunPlus hardware. These seem to run better than the other Game Key, although I suck at the Tennis game.  Again currently requires a debugger trick to boot and has various emulation issues (sound is quite bad etc.)
